name: Arohanui. Serenity in the heart of the city.
description:
Cheerful, bright two bedroom garden suite.

The moment you start down the private path to the entry of the suite you embark on an easy, calm and serene stay.

Complete restoration in 2018 in a modern, clean and open style.

I am a flight attendant and often away for work, hence I want to share my space. I am a long time resident of this area and am well versed in all Commercial Drive has to offer.

Come check it out!

The space
1970s Iconic Vancouver Special.

Very bright with views into the landscaped backyard. Switch on the heat and relax on the private covered patio with access to your own BBQ or come inside to the cozy living room and unwind with your favorite shows on Netflix.

name: Brand New 2 bed room basement
description:
Brand new suite just for you. Access to different places through transit such as Downtown Vancouver, UBC, Langara, YVR airport, Metrotown shopping centre and numerous community centres and tourist attractions.

The space
Brand new basement suite with private access, very quiet and comfortable. We have 1 queen size bed and one full size bed in two bedrooms, also one futon which can transfer to 1 queen size bed in living area.

Guest access
Guests may access the gate and the path at 1968 Nassau Drive in which leads to the spacious, brand new, and comfortable 2 bedroom 1 bathroom basement suite at 1972 Nassau Drive.

Other things to note
We also have included a spacious new kitchen with a Refrigerator, microwave, stove and oven. There is also a washer and dryer in suite.
